<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1917-07-13T07:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1917-07-13T07:00:00-05:00" n="118" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d118">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 893.00/2669</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Reinsch</persName> to
                                the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                            </hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                                    <hi rend="italic">Peking</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1917-07-13T20:00:00+08:00">
                                    <hi rend="italic">July 13, 1917, 8 p.m.</hi>
                                </date>
                            </dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>Republican troops began action against Imperialists early this morning.
                            After ten hours fighting the latter capitulated. Shan Hsun had already
                            taken refuge in the Dutch Legation. Stray bullets wounded three
                            Americans.</p>
                        <p>Tuan has already announced his Cabinet. It is to be composed; of strong
                            men representing three elements militarist, communications? [?] and Chin
                            Pu Tang. The southern Republicans are not represented. The latter are
                            dissatisfied also because of reactionary character of the cabinet.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Reinsch</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>